name: Byrne Dairy & Deli
directions: Back left hand corner
comment:
Look, this isn’t an ideal spot.  Upstate NY is very red and this is technically a truck stop.  I wouldn’t have listed it if there were better options anywhere within an hour’s drive.  All that said though, we’re open 24 hours a day, 365 days a year, and everyone who works there would take your side over some jerk giving you trouble.  If we’re not so busy that they can’t get away from the floor, people would also be willing to walk with you to the bathroom, check that there’s no one in there, and “stand guard” until you’re done.

I guess my point is that this might not be the most comfortable place to relieve yourself, but I’d bet good money that it will be *safe*.
